        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "# Optional Enhancement: company-level summary table\n",
        "\n",
        "Since you mentioned later **company/sector-based RAG**, it is useful to aggregate evidence counts by filing.\n",
        "\n",
        "```python\n",
        "df_company_signal_summary = (\n",
        "    df_evidence\n",
